.`element_name`, `ods_log`.`a`.`element_type`, `ods_log`.`a`.`ad_id`, `ods_log`.`a`.`ad_platform`, `ods_log`.`a`.`ad_source`, `ods_log`.`a`.`ad_revenue`, `ods_log`.`a`.`ad_currency_code`, `ods_log`.`a`.`ad_revenue_type`, `ods_log`.`a`.`ad_revenue_category`, `dim`.`b`.`current_language2`, `ods_log`.`a`.`app_core_ver`, `ods_log`.`a`.`ad_strategy_id`, `ods_log`.`a`.`ad_group_id`, `ods_log`.`a`.`programme_id`, `ods_log`.`a`.`module_channel_id`, `ods_log`.`a`.`etl_time`, `ods_log`.`a`.`event_strategy_id`, `ods_log`.`a`.`main_strategy_id`
